name: ORIGINAL ARTWORK
description: Dear Everyone, So basically, I have tons of one-of-a-kind, hand drawn, original Choon artwork laying around my desk that Matt and Chad are forcing me to sell. And by force I mean they talked me into it. With a knife. I'll be putting artwork up here 4 at a time, once one of them sell I'll replace it with something else. Some of them will be just random things I've drawn and colored, and some will be the original incarnations that became the designs you all now recognize. They'll be shipped to you rolled up in a protective tube, with a little authenticity note from me and a random Choonimal sticker. Thanksloveyouall Sincerely, Chris "Smooth Hand" Theibert CURRENTLY AVAILABLE: NEW ORIGINALS/PRINTS COMING SOON!
